      <p>
      &quot;William Shakespeare and His Dramatic Acts&quot; is a book written
      by Andrew Donkin in the &quot;Dead Famous&quot; series. It is a great
      little book that is very well-researched and packed with loads of
      interesting nuggets about Elizabethan England.

