      <p>
      It is very easy to
      dismiss this book as frivilous or for the children when you see it in
      a bookshop, but that would only deprive you of the pleasures this book
      holds. Apart from Shakespeare's life, this book contains amusing
      summaries of his famous plays. The illustrations are copious and are
      mostly funny.

